  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Set in the heart of the Chia Laguna Resort, Hotel Village has comfortable and spacious cottages that sit amongst lush vegetation. This hotel is ideal for families with wonderfully-appointed rooms including Family Classic Cottages that have two separate bedrooms and furnished gardens. A central pool is ideal for cooling off on those warm summer days and the rest of the resort’s facilities are close. A mini train takes you straight to the incredible white-sand beach and the lively Piazza degli Ulivi puts on entertainment most evenings. </span></p>
<p><span>Children are well-catered for at the resort with fun clubs for ages three up to 17. There’s also a nursery for babies and amenities like prams, changing mats and baby baths. Those who want to stay active will appreciate the numerous activities on offer here, including sports courts and academies for football and dance, water sports and bicycles for rent. After a busy day, relax with some bubbles at the champagne bar with views of the ocean.</span></p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Chia Laguna Resort - Hotel Village is approx. 1 hour from Cagliari airport.</p>]]></description>
